'''2019年南亚运动会'''是第13届[[南亚运动会|南亚运动会]]，于2019年12月1日至10日在[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]][[加德滿都|加德滿都]]、[[博卡拉|博卡拉]]和[[賈納克布爾|賈納克布爾]]举行<ref name=venues>{{cite news |date=2019-12-01 |title=13th South Asian Games officially begins in Kathmandu |url=https://thehimalayantimes.com/kathmandu/13th-south-asian-games-officially-begins-in-kathmandu/ |work=The Himalayan Times |location=Kathmandu, Nepal |access-date=2019-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202144713/https://thehimalayantimes.com/kathmandu/13th-south-asian-games-officially-begins-in-kathmandu/ |archive-date=2019-12-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该届比赛原定于2019年3月9日至18日举办，后来因故推迟至12月1日至10日进行，新的举办日期于2019年3月1日在[[泰国|泰国]][[曼谷|曼谷]]进行的南亚奥林匹克理事会执行委员会会议中确认<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1076301/new-date-set-for-delayed-13th-south-asian-games-in-nepal |title=New date set for delayed 13th South Asian Games in Nepal |last=Mackay |first=Duncan |date=2019-03-03 |newspaper=Inside the Games |accessdate=2019-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190326155622/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1076301/new-date-set-for-delayed-13th-south-asian-games-in-nepal |archive-date=2019-03-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/print/438581-south-asian-games-to-be-held-in-nepal-in-december |title=South Asian Games to be held in Nepal in December |newspaper=The News International |access-date=2019-03-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190326155623/https://www.thenews.com.pk/print/438581-south-asian-games-to-be-held-in-nepal-in-december |archive-date=2019-03-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。主场馆Dasarath Rangasala体育场举办开幕式、闭幕式、田径以及男子足球项目，该场馆经改建后可容纳20000名观众<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://thehimalayantimes.com/sports/nepal-host-13th-south-asian-games/ |title=Nepal to host 13th South Asian Games in March 2019 |date=2016-12-03 |access-date=2018-02-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180218150548/https://thehimalayantimes.com/sports/nepal-host-13th-south-asian-games/ |archive-date=2018-02-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

