==标志和吉祥物==
2019年5月13日，尼泊尔青年和体育部公布了该届运动会的标志及吉祥物。吉祥物为一只[[印度黑羚|印度黑羚]]，该物种在尼泊尔境内主要分布于南部地区。标志则为一只带有多种色彩尾巴的[[鸽子|鸽子]]。<ref name="sag 2019 logo">{{cite news |title=Logo and mascot of the 13th South Asian Games revealed |url=https://www.southasiatime.com/2019/05/13/logo-and-mascot-of-the-13th-south-asian-games-revealed/ |accessdate=2019-12-04 |work=South Asia Time |date=2019-05-13 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20191204183148/https://www.southasiatime.com/2019/05/13/logo-and-mascot-of-the-13th-south-asian-games-revealed/ |archivedate=2019-12-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=opening/>

