==比赛项目==
该届比赛共设26个大项<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.thenews.com.pk/print/344688-cricket-added-to-13th-south-asian-games |title=Cricket added to 13th South Asian Games |date=2018-07-22 |newspaper=The News |accessdate=2018-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007223056/https://www.thenews.com.pk/print/344688-cricket-added-to-13th-south-asian-games |archive-date=2018-10-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，其中板球时隔9年重回南亚运动会<ref name="katpost">{{cite news|url=http://kathmandupost.ekantipur.com/news/2018-07-22/cricket-returns-after-8-years.html|title=13th South Asian Games: Cricket returns after 8 years|first=Prajwal|last=Oli|date=2018-07-22|newspaper=The Kathmandu Post|accessdate=2018-10-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181007223119/http://kathmandupost.ekantipur.com/news/2018-07-22/cricket-returns-after-8-years.html|archive-date=2018-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>，高尔夫和空手道为主办方自行加入的大项<ref name="katpost"/>。每个比赛大项必须有至少4个国家参加，否则该大项不会举办。滑翔伞原本为该届比赛的大项之一，然而由于仅有两个国家（尼泊尔和巴基斯坦）有合资格选手，该大项最终被剔除<ref>{{cite news |date=2019-11-21 |title=No paragliding competition in 13th South Asian Games |url=https://english.khabarhub.com/2019/21/56653/ |work=Khabarhub |location=Kathmandu, Nepal |access-date=2019-11-30 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927045909/https://english.khabarhub.com/2019/21/56653/ }}</ref>。

